A core contribution would be a principled framework for valid, semantics-preserving transformations in combinatorial, rule-bound domains, addressing gaps compared to conventional augmentation in vision tasks. This approach also mitigates training biases (e.g., overrepresentation of aggressive strategies) via strategy-mix synthesis, enhancing performance across diverse opponents.

